  <name>GnomeQS</name>
  <summary>GNOME-first Quick Share client for Linux</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      GnomeQS is a Quick Share client for Linux designed primarily for GNOME,
      with a GTK4 and libadwaita interface focused on nearby device discovery
      and local file sharing.
    </p>
    <p>
      It lets you send and receive files with nearby devices from a desktop
      interface that fits modern GNOME environments, with configurable
      visibility and packaging for native Linux distribution workflows.
    </p>
  </description>
